Usage: routePGPinUseSignalRoute [-help] [-all] [-maxFanout <integer>]
                                [-nets <string>] [-nonDefaultRule <string>]
                                [-pattern {trunk steiner}] [-well]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-all                              # route all non-primary power/ground pins
                                  # (bool, optional)
-maxFanout <integer>              # cluster size (int, optional)
-nets <string>                    # list of nets (string, optional)
-nonDefaultRule <string>          # rule name (string, optional)
-pattern {trunk steiner}          # route pattern (enum, optional)
-well                             # include nwell and pwell pins
                                  # (bool, optional)